The Palo Alto community is sharing its memories of Palo Alto High School science teacher Kenyon Scott, <a href="http://palyvoice.com/2016/01/07/community-mourns-teacher-death/">who died of unidentified natural causes on Jan. 6 in his home.</a> Photos by William Zhou, Bianca Al-Shamari, Sam Lee and Takaaki Sagawa.

<iframe src="//www.cincopa.com/media-platform/iframe.aspx?fid=AILABMtesoWk" width="600" height="430" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe>

&nbsp;

With ongoing gym construction at Palo Alto High School, the 2016 Winter Rally featured a staff-vs.-student soccer game. The staff beat the seniors, 3-2, and the Associated Student Body announced the Prom 2016 location to be the Design Galleria in San Francisco. Watch the highlights of the game.

